title: Identification of Pastures by Province, Afghanistan, NRVA 2003
name: Identification of Pastures by Province, Afghanistan, NRVA 2003
description:
Sources: NRVA 2003 as analysed by AREU.
This shapefiles shows the number of pastures indicated for summer/winter/recent permanent/total, as well as the percent by type of pastures for 19 different provinces in Afghanistan.
